Like No Other

OUR BRIEF HISTORY

Royal Bonanza Since 1976

Restaurants are popular in the area known as Le Midi. Oysters come from the
Etang de Thau, to be served in the restaurants of Bouzigues, Meze, and Ste.
Mussels are commonly seen here in addition.

Pizza Margherita

Penne pasta with sauted bell peppers and romano in our roasted red pepper sauce.

Penne Monte Cristo

Our thick 'n hearty burger on a toasted bakery bun. Served with lettuce, tomato and love.

Big Tommy Burger

Onion rings, HBC sauce, peppered pastrami, Swiss cheese, lettuce, served with a gherkin. SEE WHAT WERE COOKING

Our Food Gallery
